deploymanteau
=============
A collection of tools to help automate the deployment of a static website
 using stagit to create static HTML pages of the repos to be hosted by a
 simple HTTP server such as darkhttpd or quark.

This program is broken down into three key functions
	* add    - add a new repo to be monitored
	* deploy - refresh all of the repos
	* update - update a single repo passed as a paramater
